This paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) category as it deals with deep reinforcement learning and neural networks. It could also belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) category as it proposes a new algorithm for improving RL. The paper also involves robotics (cs.RO) as it experiments on the Cartpole problem, which is a classic control problem in robotics. The paper also deals with control systems (cs.SY) as it proposes a new algorithm for stabilizing greediness in RL. Finally, the paper involves neural networks (cs.NE) as it combines CPI with deep RL using neural networks.
